creator: OfficeR&D
descriptionHtml: Metropolitan Workspace is unique for its Affordability, Flexibility, Mobility and Diversity. We cater for all types of entrepreneurs, freelancers to corporates. There is a wide range of membership plans with tailored pricing and service options. We allow you to move around in different parts of Hong Kong, and we welcome people of different nationalities, background and professions.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Metro Workspace comes with a new slick design and improved usability. Highlights:
- A branded welcome screen that offers quick access to the most important actions and community posts
- A simple bookings experience with nice meeting room visuals, easily accessible filters, and intuitive booking editing and cancelation flows
- Quick access to the most important activities and guides in your community including Support Tickets, Events, Companies, Members, Benefits and How-to guides

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
Metro Workspace’s latest release comes with the following improvements:
- Members can now publish posts in on the community news feed
- Members can now submit general questions or issues with the building, that will be directly received by their Building Manager (Tickets). They can also track and reply to all of their submitted tickets
- Custom pages type text or member wall that were available on the web portal are now available in the app
